Jordan Spieth a Amurka 5&4 ya yi watsi da daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Jagoran duniya, Edo Johnson, ya fadi a 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
A cikin Ryder Cups guda takwas, Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama zakara a gasar Turai a cikin minti 25.5.
