Ya mika kwallo ga dan wasansa John Ram wanda ya doke dan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasan daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, ɗan shekara 23 ya ce: "Na yi alfahari sosai da na ci Tiger Woods, kuma na girma ina kallon mutumin.
Gundumar ta rasa wasanni hudu a Faransa kuma tana da tarihin Ryder Cup na 13-21-3 a duk lokacin da ta yi wasa.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na kowane lokaci, inda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14 kuma na biyu ne kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
Kungiyar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya a duk karshen mako don neman hotunan gidan wasan tare da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka kasance manyan 'yan wasan golf a duk lokacin gasar.
Bayan wani gagarumin wasan kwaikwayon da sojojinsa suka yi, Janar Jim Furyk na Amirka ya ce: "Ina alfahari da waɗannan samarin da suka yi yaƙi.
