Sabuntawa na Red Wave: An rage sa ido ga Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka bayar kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa Red Tide yana raguwa a yankunan yankin Tampa Bay.
<seg id="3">A cewar FWC, ana samun rahoton yanayin iskar gas a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma wasu yankuna masu zaman kansu - wanda ke nuna rashin tsaro.
Red Tide yana da nisan mil 130 daga bakin teku daga arewacin Pinella zuwa kudu na Lee.
Ana iya ganin raƙuman ruwa na mil 10 daga cikin gundumar Hillsborough County, amma a wurare kaɗan ne kawai ba a taɓa ganin su ba a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma bincika Red Tide a Pasco County.
An bayar da rahoton a makon da ya gabata cewa an samu wasu wurare masu nisa a cikin Pinellas County, da ke kusa da Hillsborough County, da ke kusa da Manatee County, da ke kusa da Sarasota County, da ke kusa da Charlotte County, da kuma a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni daga Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma yawan wuraren da ake amfani da su.
Ba a samu rahoton ciwon numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
